 chants to those of other Mazatec shamans, and more.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 4acontemporary. 4ahistory of art. 4athe arts. 7aART / History / Modern (late 19th Century to 1945).2bisacsh1 aAridjis, Homero, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEstrada, Alvaro, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aEstrada, Álvaro, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGordon Wasson, R., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMunn, Henry, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPavlovna Wasson, Valentina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRegino, Juan Gregorio, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRichardson, Allan.1 aRothenberg, Jerome, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRothenberg, Jerome, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWaldman, Anne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z97831106904220 cprintz978052023953140uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052034200240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520342002423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520342002/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles